00:27.695 --> 00:29.762
I'm Helen Mirren,
and you're watching

00:29.764 --> 00:33.799
"Documentary Now!"
Season 51.

00:33.801 --> 00:37.770
For a decade, Test Pattern
combined new wave music,

00:37.772 --> 00:40.773
performance art,
and political activism

00:40.775 --> 00:44.543
to become one of the world's
most famous rock bands.

00:44.545 --> 00:48.614
And then, suddenly, it was over.

00:48.616 --> 00:51.250
But not before one last concert,

00:51.252 --> 00:55.587
forever preserved in the film
"Final Transmission."

