13:00.514 --> 13:02.781
♪ In ding, in ding... ♪

13:09.189 --> 13:11.422
♪ In ding, in ding... ♪

13:19.165 --> 13:22.233
For you, creativity seems
to be your primary concern.

13:22.235 --> 13:24.502
Would you say that
you resent your success?

13:24.504 --> 13:26.304
I don't know
that I'm successful.

13:26.306 --> 13:27.305
I don't know that.

13:27.307 --> 13:29.340
I'm always yearning.

13:29.342 --> 13:31.176
That's just what I do...
I just keep trying

13:31.178 --> 13:32.811
to make more things and...

13:32.813 --> 13:34.512
I have no resentment because...

13:34.514 --> 13:36.414
well, I do have
some resentment.

13:36.416 --> 13:39.017
But that's a separate issue.

13:44.558 --> 13:48.159
